<%@ Page Title="About Kumari Cinemas" Language="C#" MasterPageFile="~/Site.Master" AutoEventWireup="true" CodeBehind="About.aspx.cs" Inherits="StudentManagementSystem.About" %>

<asp:Content ID="BodyContent" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent" runat="server">
    <main aria-labelledby="title">
        <h2 id="title"><%: Title %></h2>
        <hr />
        
        <h3>Revolutionizing the Movie Experience in Nepal</h3>
        <p>
            Kumari Cinemas is a premier cinema chain dedicated to establishing a new standard for entertainment across Nepal. 
            Our mission is to overcome traditional industry challenges—such as high operational costs and poor customer experiences—by 
            introducing sophisticated, world-class movie halls in cities like Pokhara, Biratnagar, and beyond[cite: 69, 79].
        </p>

        <h3>Our Centralized System</h3>
        <p>
            To ensure a seamless journey for our patrons, we have implemented a robust, centralized management system[cite: 70, 71]. 
            This automation-driven platform allows us to:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Efficient Ticket Management:</strong> Registered users can easily book or buy multiple tickets for any of our locations[cite: 72].</li>
            <li><strong>Smart Automation:</strong> Our system features an automated cancellation policy; reserved seats are released if tickets are not purchased 1 hour prior to showtime[cite: 73].</li>
            <li><strong>Optimized Scheduling:</strong> We manage diverse showtimes—including Morning, Day, and Evening slots—tailored to the latest movie releases.</li>
            <li><strong>Dynamic Pricing:</strong> We ensure fair and transparent pricing, with adjustments for public holidays and blockbuster release weeks[cite: 74].</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Our Locations</h3>
        <p>
            Whether you are visiting us at <strong>Pokhara Cineplex</strong>, <strong>Labim Mall</strong>, or <strong>Kumari Cinemas Biratnagar</strong>, 
            we guarantee a high-capacity, comfortable, and technically advanced environment for every screening.
        </p>
    </main>
</asp:Content>